data.description: This charming condo flat in the desirable West Ashley area boasts an open floor plan with three sizable bedrooms and two bathrooms. You are greeted with a welcoming living room that flows into the spacious kitchen. This condo is lit with tons of natural light that flows in from the numerous windows. You are greeted with tons of storage space as each bedroom is accompanied by a walk-in closet, with several storage closets placed strategically throughout the condo. This property is a must-see with its location only 15 minutes from downtown Charleston.
